            <title>[LU-5482] lustre-tests rpm need to depend on rsync and attr</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5482</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Tests use get/setfattr and rsync but never require these pkg to install.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
